Description:

It ain't secret no more... After a ten year tenure as one of the brightest stars in the constellation of adult video, you'd think a superstar like Nina Hartley wouldn't have any secrets left to share. Of course you'd be dead wrong. Here, in celebration of a decade of delicious performances. Nina finally lives out her unfulfilled fantasies with a handpicked dream cast. A true labor of love from start to finish, The Secret Life of Nina Hartley was written and directed by Nina herself to bring her fans a truly erotic look at the inner desires of a living legend. Discover a side of Nina you never knew existed. Discover the life of Nina Hartley
